title: American Paintings - An Illustrated Catalogue (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
American Paintings: An Illustrated Catalogue
National Gallery of Art | 1980 | ISBN 0894681710 | English | 324 pages | pdf | 33.6 MB


In an institution devoted to collecting and exhibiting great works from the whole Western tradition, it is appropriate that art receive thoughtful attention. This new illustrated summary catalogue is intended as a source of both pleasure and edification for all who consult it
